DTField.Name: USEPRICELIST
DTField.Label: USEPRICELIST
DTField.DTFieldHelp: Dropdown - Determines the connection between the price to charge modifier (time/quantity) and the basis on which to charge (None/Price/Time/Both): No – Use the price per unit (price list is irrelevant). Billing Basis – The billing basis determines the units to retrieve a price from the Price List. Bill by Days –The number of days that a load determines the units to retrieve a price from the Price List. Bill Basis by Day – determines that the Price List will be used to define a price for the storage period, while the actual charge will be created according to the relative period that the Load was in storage.
